lemma eq_bot_iff_card {G : Type*} [Group G] {H : Subgroup G} [Fintype H] :

    simpa [eq_bot_iff_forall, card_eq_one_iff]
  constructor
  ¬∑ intro h
    use 1, H.one_mem
  ¬∑ rintro ‚ü®y, -, hy'‚ü© x hx
    calc x = y := hy' x hx
    _      = 1 := (hy' 1 H.one_mem).symm

    H = ‚ä• ‚Üî card H = 1    := by

  exact ‚ü®fun h => ‚ü®1, H.one_mem, h‚ü©, fun ‚ü®y, _, hy‚ü© x hx => (hy x hx).trans (hy 1 H.one_mem).symm‚ü©
